Leaf: Bellabeat’s classic wellness tracker can be worn as a bracelet, necklace, or clip. The Leaf tracker connects to the Bellabeat app to track 1. activity, 2. sleep, and 3. stress.
Time: This wellness watch combines the timeless look of a classic timepiece with smart technology to track user 1. activity, 2. sleep, and 3. stress. The Time watch connects to the Bellabeat app to provide you with insights into your daily wellness.
