Prompt:
How can I eliminate blank rows in excel?

Find & Select > Go To Special. A “Go To Special” window will open. Here, enable the “Blanks” option, then choose “OK” at the bottom. All the blank rows in your selected dataset are now highlighted.


Prompt:
How can I get distinct values in excel?

Data, filter, Advanced, click on Unique Values Only
Conditional formatting, unique values…

Prompt:
How can I separate datetime into date and time?
=FIND
=LEFT
=RIGHT
=MID
=LEN

Or convert it to text and then use Data, Split (excel: Text to column)
How can I convert datetime to text?

=TEXT (A2, “dd/mm/yyyy mm:hh”)


